	<element name="Barrier Techniques" type="Class Feature" source="JJK" id="ID_JJK_CLASS_FEATURE_SUPPORT_SPECIALIST_BARRIER_TECHNIQUES">
		<requirements>!ID_INTERNAL_FEATURE_REPLACEMENT_SUPPORT_SPECIALIST_BARRIER_TECHNIQUES</requirements>
		<description>
			<p>At 2nd level, you have learned how to create basic barriers to protect areas or trap opponents and protect allies. As an action for up to your Cursed Energy modifier in cursed energy, you make a dome starting from yourself with a 5-foot radius and a 10-foot height. For each cursed energy spent, the barrier can increase its width by 10 feet and its height by 10 feet. This barrier has 10 hit points per cursed energy spent and is immune to Poison and Psychic damage. This barrier lasts a number of minutes equal to your Cursed Energy modifier. At 9th level, your barriers have health equal to 20 times the cursed energy spent, and at 15th level it is resistant to damage from the outside.</p>
		</description>
		<sheet usage="Action">
			<description level="2">Up to {{ce:modifier}} in cursed energy, you make a dome starting from yourself with a 5-foot radius and a 10-foot height. For each cursed energy spent, the barrier can increase its width by 10 feet and its height by 10 feet. This barrier has 10 hit points per cursed energy spent and is immune to Poison and Psychic damage. This barrier lasts {{ce:modifier}} minutes.</description>
			<description level="9">Up to {{ce:modifier}} in cursed energy, you make a dome starting from yourself with a 5-foot radius and a 10-foot height. For each cursed energy spent, the barrier can increase its width by 10 feet and its height by 10 feet. This barrier has 20 hit points per cursed energy spent and is immune to Poison and Psychic damage. This barrier lasts {{ce:modifier}} minutes.</description>
			<description level="15">Up to {{ce:modifier}} in cursed energy, you make a dome starting from yourself with a 5-foot radius and a 10-foot height. For each cursed energy spent, the barrier can increase its width by 10 feet and its height by 10 feet. This barrier has 20 hit points per cursed energy spent and is immune to Poison and Psychic damage and is resistant to damage from the outside. This barrier lasts {{ce:modifier}} minutes.</description>
		</sheet>
	</element>
	<element name="Ability Score Improvement" type="Class Feature" source="JJK" id="ID_JJK_CLASS_FEATURE_SUPPORT_SPECIALIST_ABILITYSCOREIMPROVEMENT_SUPPORT_SPECIALIST">
		<requirements>!ID_INTERNAL_FEATURE_REPLACEMENT_SUPPORT_SPECIALIST_ABILITYSCOREIMPROVEMENT_SUPPORT_SPECIALIST</requirements>
		<compendium display="false" />
		<description>
			<p>When you reach 4th level, and again at 6th, 8th, 10th, 12th, 16th, and 19th level, you can increase one ability score of your choice by 2, or you can increase two ability scores of your choice by 1. As normal, you can’t increase an ability score above 20 using this feature.</p>
		</description>
		<sheet display="false" />
		<rules>
			<select type="Class Feature" name="Improvement Option (Strategist 4)" supports="Improvement Option,Strategist,4" level="4" />
			<select type="Class Feature" name="Improvement Option (Strategist 6)" supports="Improvement Option,Strategist,6" level="6" />
			<select type="Class Feature" name="Improvement Option (Strategist 8)" supports="Improvement Option,Strategist,8" level="8" />
			<select type="Class Feature" name="Improvement Option (Strategist 10)" supports="Improvement Option,Strategist,10" level="10" />
			<select type="Class Feature" name="Improvement Option (Strategist 12)" supports="Improvement Option,Strategist,12" level="12" />
			<select type="Class Feature" name="Improvement Option (Strategist 16)" supports="Improvement Option,Strategist,16" level="16" />
			<select type="Class Feature" name="Improvement Option (Strategist 19)" supports="Improvement Option,Strategist,19" level="19" />
		</rules>
	</element>
	<element name="Sorcerous Restoration" type="Class Feature" source="JJK" id="ID_JJK_CLASS_FEATURE_SUPPORT_SPECIALIST_REVERSE_CURSE_TECHNIQUE">
		<requirements>!ID_INTERNAL_FEATURE_REPLACEMENT_SUPPORT_SPECIALIST_REVERSE_CURSE_TECHNIQUE</requirements>
		<description>
			<p>At 15th level, you regain 4 cursed energy on a short rest.</p>
		</description>
		<sheet>
			<description>You regain 4 cursed energy on a short rest.</description>
		</sheet>
	</element>
	<element name="Signature Move" type="Class Feature" source="JJK" id="ID_JJK_CLASS_FEATURE_SUPPORT_SPECIALIST_REVERSE_TECHNIQUE_UNDERSTANDING">
		<requirements>!ID_INTERNAL_FEATURE_REPLACEMENT_SUPPORT_SPECIALIST_REVERSE_TECHNIQUE_UNDERSTANDING</requirements>
		<description>
			<p>At 20th level, you can choose a feature that uses cursed energy, that is not a domain expansion, maximum, or reverse curse technique, and makes it have no cursed energy cost. It counts as the minimum input of Cursed Energy necessary.</p>
		</description>
		<sheet>
			<description>You can choose a feature that uses cursed energy, that is not a domain expansion, maximum, or reverse curse technique, and makes it have no cursed energy cost. It counts as the minimum input of Cursed Energy necessary.</description>
		</sheet>
